{"tid":135811,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【差佬晒馬】以色列主要報章：港警引發外交事件","createTime":"2017-02-26T15:18:37.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-27T14:20:15.000Z","uid":11001,"like":59,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5b82fa501ed0709b098a8602c194b0d484da49d6","tid":135811,"uid":11001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T15:18:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170226/large/1488121634_321c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170226%2Flarge%2F1488121634_321c.jpg&h=a9a47ee6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有警員以納粹德軍迫害的猶太人事件比喻警員被侮辱，事件繼續發酵，連以色列主要報章亦有報道事件。以色列《國土報》（Haaretz）報道中，以「不明智」（ill-advised）來形容有香港警察在大型集會（mass protest）中，自比被納粹德軍迫害的猶太人，直言香港警隊面臨外交事件（faced a type of a diplomatic incident）。<br />\n<br />\n該報道於2月26日發表，標題為《Hong Kong Police Face Israeli, German Backlash After Comparing Local Cops to Jews Persecuted by Nazis（將當地警察比作被納粹迫害的猶太人 港警面臨以色列及德國反彈）》，主要轉述本港《南華早報》早前報道，指警察協會特別大會上，有人將警員的遭遇自比在二戰中受到迫害的猶太人，其後德國駐港總領事館及以色列領事館等分別發表聲明指言論不恰當。報道又引述《南華早報》報道消息指，警隊高層計劃聯絡以色列及德國兩個駐港總領事館澄清有關言論不代表警方立場，擔心事件影響香港警隊的國際形象，甚至引發外交風波。<br />\n<br />\n「國師」陳雲在facebook轉貼《國土報》報道，並在帖文中寫道：「皇天有眼！以色列主流報紙Haaretz專題報導香港警察叛亂及侮辱猶太人的事，以色列當局正在考慮向香港發出正式外交抗議。家醜外傳，香港揚威國際，習近平先生有排煩。」<br />\n<br />\n《國土報》報道連結：<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2lXQjFw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2lXQjFw&d=gHNHb7VIn83nczLIzOZu1cmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=712fa087\" target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2lXQjFw</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20170226/56357483\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20170226%2F56357483&d=gHNHb7VIn83nczLIzOZu1cmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=3976bd14\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20170226%2F56357483&h=6e9a6b5f\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20170226/56357483</a>"},{"pid":"24bc6b97f7b9fa5d99a5d849a4e02c06d463732e","tid":135811,"uid":11001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T15:18:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20170226/56357483\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20170226%2F56357483&d=gHNHb7VIn83nczLIzOZu1cmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=3976bd14\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20170226%2F56357483&h=6e9a6b5f\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20170226/56357483</a>"},{"pid":"80dfc17f8c8ad040fe33eb51503c850df708d58d","tid":135811,"uid":28277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T15:21:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25f03606a0a070b03cbea88bf9ab2311222088c5","tid":135811,"uid":60831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T15:22:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8682f42b03ca65ac4e3abe7f1fc5e0c6a3ffeaec","tid":135811,"uid":62815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T15:23:20.000Z","msg":"繼續推唔好停<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3760a4fcbaf7da1faa1832033a0448f10c95a270","tid":135811,"uid":693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T15:24:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"652b0498905f7705fd83c34f43b4b16d59f0890a","tid":135811,"uid":22858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-